  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "I want to activate my old whatsapp but I'm over seas and have the old number?",
  "response": "If you're trying to use WhatsApp with an old phone number while overseas, you have a few options, but they depend on whether you still have access to that number or if it's been reassigned. Here's what you can do:\n\n### Option 1: If You Still Have Access to the Old Number\nIf you can still receive SMS or calls on the old number, you can use it to verify your account:\n\n1. **Ensure Access to the Old Number**: Make sure you can temporarily use the old number (e.g., by using a dual SIM phone or a SIM card swapper if you have the SIM).\n2. **Install WhatsApp**: Download and install WhatsApp on your device.\n3. **Verification**: Open WhatsApp, enter your old number, and wait for the verification code. Enter the code to activate WhatsApp.\n\n### Option 2: If You No Longer Have Access to the Old Number\nIf the old number has been reassigned and you can't receive the verification code:\n\n1. **Request WhatsApp Support**: Contact WhatsApp support and explain your situation. They might be able to help you regain access to your account, although this isn't guaranteed.\n2. **Use Email Verification**: Some versions of WhatsApp allow verification via email. If this option is available, you can use it to regain access.\n3. **Start Fresh**: If all else fails, you may need to start a new WhatsApp account with your current number. Unfortunately, you won't be able to restore your old chats without the old number.\n\n### Additional Tips:\n- **Backup Your Chats**: If you're switching numbers or devices, make sure to back up your WhatsApp chats to avoid losing your conversation history.\n- **Dual SIM or eSIM**: If your device supports dual SIM or eSIM, you can keep your old number active temporarily just for the verification process.\n\nRemember, WhatsApp's policies regarding account verification and recovery can change, so it's always a good idea to check their official support pages for the most current information.",
